Each TruStacks image is signed via Sigstore keyless OIDC. Verify with:

    cosign verify \
      --certificate-identity-regexp \
        'https://github.com/TruStacks/trustacks-mvp/.github/workflows/publish-images.yml@refs/tags/v[0-9]+\.[0-9]+\.[0-9]+(-[0-9A-Za-z.-]+)?$' \
      --certificate-oidc-issuer https://token.actions.githubusercontent.com \
      ghcr.io/trustacks/<image>:<version>

SBOMs are attached to each image manifest via buildx's `sbom: true`
output. Query with:

    docker buildx imagetools inspect \
      ghcr.io/trustacks/<image>:<version> \
      --format '{{ json .SBOM }}'

